# Example environment for tachos-ru. Copy to `.env.local` and fill in.
# Only NEXT_PUBLIC_* values reach the browser. The site is a static export
# (GitHub Pages), so there is no server runtime here — secrets that must stay
# private belong in the serverless function, not in this file.

# --- Feedback form ---
# Endpoint of the serverless function that receives feedback and opens a GitHub
# Issue (see FEEDBACK_FOR_VADIM.md for the contract). Leave empty to run the
# form in demo mode: it validates and shows success but sends nothing.
NEXT_PUBLIC_FEEDBACK_ENDPOINT=""
